  "texts": [
    "We primarily analyzed VideoQA with exo-centric datasets -videos from the third-person view.",
    "It should be noted that an important real-world application for VideoQA is geared towards reliable embodied assistance (Grauman et al., 2022; Majumdar et al., 2024).",
    "In this regard, ego-centric, or first-person view videos and associated question-answer pairs are of great interest and relevance.",
    "3.8.2 shows that Video-LLMs pre-trained on third-person view VideoQA datasets can generalize to these application scenarios.",
    "However, their performance is weak compared with the tool-based Video-LLMs (Zhang et al., 2023a) that directly use ego-centric pretrained visual descriptions (Zhao et al., 2023), and well-prompted general-purpose MLLMs (e.g."
  ]
}